---
title: Roasted Pork Chops in Apple Apricot Sauce with Sugar Snap Peas and Butter Rice
description: Fruit and pork go together like peas and carrots! This sauce doubles down on that, offering a fresh apple and apricot preserve sauce. Served with buttery rice and snappy peas.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cotelettes-de-porc-roties-et-sauce-a-labricot-et-a-la-pomme-12510ce9.jpg
